    </item>
    <item>
      <title>[두근두근 뇌 운동] [2905] 퍼즐 맞추기</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/nie/2026/07/10/WONEQFQAC5AKXOLX4JS3YNNPFU/</link>
